{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/BVDecide/Normalize/AndFlatten.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.andFlatteningPass\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">BVDecide</span>.<span class=\"name\">Normalize</span>.<span class=\"name\">andFlatteningPass</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/BVDecide/Normalize/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.Pass\">Pass</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Flatten out ands. That is look for hypotheses of the form `h : (x && y) = true` and replace them\nwith `h.left : x = true` and `h.right : y = true`. This can enable more fine grained substitutions\nin embedded constraint substitution.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/BVDecide/Normalize/AndFlatten.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.andFlatteningPass","kind":"def","line":30,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.andFlatteningPass","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/BVDecide/Normalize/AndFlatten.lean#L30-L109"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.Basic","Std.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.Bool"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.BVDecide.Normalize.AndFlatten"}